 is aimed at realistic Boxing games using virtual reality systems.\nIf you want to enjoy Boxing through VR, Manny Boxing VR will be a choice without regret!\n\nfeatures\n\u25cfBoxing play with Manny Pacquiao\n\u25cfVarious boxing training modes\n- Mitt training ( with Manny )\n- Dummy hitting practice\n- Punching speed ball\n- Heavy Bag Training\n\n\u25cf Advanced AI divided by 5 difficulty levels\n\u25cf Multiplayer boxing in real-time\n\nhow to Play\nBoxing is a Dynamic sport played using gloves to hit opponent in the Boxing ring.\nAvoiding the opponent's attack, Attack your opponent in various ways.\n\nChallenge the best boxers!", "short_description": "Manny Pacquiao is the only eight-division world champion in the history of boxing and has won twelve major world titles. Enjoy boxing with world-renowned boxing star, Manny Pacquiao! Realistic physics, immersive sound, and fluid animation make you feel like you\u2019re really in the Boxing ring."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.appnori.com/policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Appnori Inc.", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.appnori.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2776542286000603"}, {"id": "331529188132278"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["CASUAL", "SIMULATION", "SPORTS"], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "zh_CN"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER", "MULTI_USER"], "id": "860418018440834"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 3, "nodes